@node Reporting Slowness
@section Reporting Slowness

Users are encouraged to report any significant slowness of Kasten! If possible,
please include the following information, but please @strong{do not include any
sensitive information}:
@itemize
@item
Emacs version (@kbd{M-x emacs-version @key{RET}})
@item
Kasten version
@item
Operating system (@samp{uname -a})
@item
Number of indexed files (@samp{ls -1 /path/to/notes | wc -l})
@item
Total size of indexed files (@samp{du -sh /path/to/notes})
